                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211024-141-off820 t18211024-141-cd821"></join>, one watch, value 10 s.; one coat, value 5 s., and one pair of shoes, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18211024-141-victim1297" type="victimName">
