                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman of <placeName id="t18211024-141-crimeloc823">St. Giles's</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18211024-141-crimeloc823" type="placeName" value="St. Giles's"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18211024-141-crimeloc823" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211024-141-off820 t18211024-141-crimeloc823"></join>. I had information against the prisoner, I knew he lived at this house. I saw him several nights, but could not overtake him, he left after this, and I took him on the 11th of October, in a court in St. Giles's - I knew he and Sullivan lived together at the same house.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18211024-141-person1300">
                  JOHN 
                  HEWSON
               <interp inst="t18211024-141-person1300" type="surname" value="HEWSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211024-141-person1300" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211024-141-person1300" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I went to the house after him, but could not find him, except at night, when he was in company with four or five bad characters.</p>
